curam.util.persistence.helper

Interface LinkTable<L extends StandardEntity,R extends StandardEntity>

  • Type Parameters:
    L - The type of the "left-hand side" entity.
    R - The type of the "right-hand side" entity.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Entity<java.lang.Long>, Insertable, Removable, StandardEntity
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LinkTableImpl

    public interface LinkTable<L extends StandardEntity,R extends StandardEntity>
extends StandardEntity, Insertable, Removable
    A simple link table. Which has:
    • its own primary key; and
    • two mandatory foreign keys, referred to here as the:
      • "left-hand side" ; and
      • "right-hand side"
